sequenceDiagram
    %% ===== 页面渲染：manual 优先级裁决 =====
    actor Crawler
    participant Page as 详情页(generateMetadata)
    participant DB as Prisma/PostgreSQL
    participant Resolve as resolvePageKeywords
    participant Auto as seo-keywords.ts

    Crawler->>Page: 请求 /[locale]/products|blog/...
    Page->>DB: findFirst(select 含 seoKeywords)
    DB-->>Page: product/blog + seoKeywords(Json?)
    Page->>Auto: buildDetailPageKeywords(title, slug)
    Auto-->>Page: auto: string[]
    Page->>Resolve: resolvePageKeywords({manual, auto, locale})
    alt manual[locale] 非空
        Resolve-->>Page: 返回 manual(原样, 不过滤)
    else manual[locale] 空/缺失
        Resolve-->>Page: 返回 auto
    end
    Page-->>Crawler: <meta name="keywords" content="...">

    %% ===== 后台保存：归一化落库 =====
    actor Admin
    participant UI as admin add/edit 表单(三语框)
    participant API as /api/admin/products|blogs
    participant Norm as normalizeSeoKeywords
    participant DB2 as blog_posts / products

    Admin->>UI: 填 en/zh/ar 关键词
    UI->>API: POST/PUT {seoKeywords:{en,zh,ar}}
    API->>Norm: normalizeSeoKeywords(body.seoKeywords)
    Norm-->>API: {en,zh,ar} 字符串
    API->>DB2: upsert seoKeywords(JsonB)
    DB2-->>API: ok

    %% ===== 一次性种子脚本 =====
    actor Operator
    participant Script as scripts/seed-keywords.mjs
    participant CSV as 关键词表格(csv/json)
    participant DB3 as blog_posts / products

    Operator->>Script: node seed-keywords.mjs --file x.csv --mode merge
    Script->>CSV: 读取行(entity,slug,keywords_*)
    loop 每行
        Script->>DB3: findFirst(slug)
        DB3-->>Script: 现有 seoKeywords
        Script->>DB3: update seoKeywords(仅补空语言)
    end
